   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 13th(?) year of Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Caesar the lord. Kastor, son of Ptol . . ., has paid for the monodesmia of hay and other charges, through the elders of Stratonos, eight drachmai twelve obols, equals 8 drachmai 12 obols.</ab>
